I want a
semi-freaking-normal life.

6
00:00:10.560 --> 00:00:13.673
<i>Medical examiner determines
killer of girl to be animal. not human.</i>

7
00:00:13.697 --> 00:00:16.481
Derek not killer.
Let out of jail.

8
00:00:16.550 --> 00:00:18.578
You did this to me!
The bite is a gift.

9
