<i>♪ Pushin' the unmovable clouds</i>

27
00:01:20.414 --> 00:01:23.565
<i>♪ I know I have
to make it somehow</i>

28
00:01:24.601 --> 00:01:26.968
<i>♪ Flyin' like an airplane</i>

29
00:01:28.405 --> 00:01:32.457
<i>♪ Faster than the fallin' rain</i>

30
00:01:32.526 --> 00:01:36.194
<i>♪ My brain is in
