31
00:01:36.263 --> 00:01:39.064
<i>♪ Scattered in American crowds ♪</i>

32
00:01:57.268 --> 00:01:58.533
What's wrong?

33
00:02:01.055 --> 00:02:02.055
Get away.

34
00:02:02.122 --> 00:02:03.371
Scott?

35
00:02:09.896 --> 00:02:12.331
Scott? Get away from me.

36
00:03:06.753 --> 00:03:08.753
So you killed her? I don't know.

37
00:03:08.822 --> 00:03:10.355
I just woke up.

38
00:03:10.424 --> 00:03:12.536
And I was sweating like
crazy. and I couldn't breathe.

39
00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.437
I've never had a dream
where I woke up like that before.

40
00:03:14.461 --> 00:03:15.760
Really? I have.

41
00:03:15.829 --> 00:03:17.707
Usually ends a
little differently.

42
00:03:17.731 --> 00:03:19.643
A. I meant I've never had
a dream that felt that real.

43
00:03:19.667 --> 00:03:22.379
and B. never give me that much
detail about you in bed again.

44
00:03:22.403 --> 00:03:24.702
Noted. Let me take a guess here.

45
00:03:24.771 --> 00:03:26.505
No. I know.

46
00:03:26.573 --> 00:03:28.385
you think it has something to do with
me going out with Allison tomorrow.

47
00:03:28.409 --> 00:03:29.886
Like I'm gonna lose
control and rip her throat out.

48
00:03:29.910 --> 00:03:31.576
No. of course not.

49
00:03:32.312 --> 00:03:34.612
Yeah. that's totally it.

50
00:03:34.681 --> 00:03:36.682
Hey. come on. it's
gonna be fine. all right?

51
00:03:36.750 --> 00:03:39.295
Personally. I think you're handling
this pretty freaking amazingly.

52
00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:40.680
You know. it's not like there's

53
00:03:40.704 --> 00:03:43.471
a Lycanthropy for
Beginners class you can take.

54
00:03:43.540 --> 00:03:46.240
Yeah. not a class.
but maybe a teacher.

55
00:03:46.309 --> 00:03:48.810
Who. Derek?

56
00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:50.623
You forgetting the part where
we got him tossed in jail?

57
00:03:50.647 --> 00:03:52.892
Yeah. I know. but chasing her.

58
00:03:52.916 --> 00:03:55.060
dragging her to the back
of the bus. it felt so real.

59
00:03:55.084 --> 00:03:56.384
How real?

60
