So I hear they're saying it's
some type of animal attack.

124
00:08:04.134 --> 00:08:06.061
Probably a cougar. I
heard mountain lion.

125
00:08:06.085 --> 00:08:09.670
A cougar is a
mountain lion. Isn't it?

126
00:08:09.739 --> 00:08:11.756
Who cares?

127
00:08:11.825 --> 00:08:13.235
The guy's probably some homeless
tweaker who's gonna die anyway.

128
00:08:13.259 --> 00:08:16.978
Actually. I just found
out who it is. Check it out.

129
00:08:17.047 --> 00:08:19.992
<i>The Sheriff's Department won't
speculate on details of the incident</i>

130
00:08:20.016 --> 00:08:23.652
<i>but confirmed the victim. Garrison
Meyers. did survive the attack.</i>

131
00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:25.548
<i>Meyers was taken
to a local hospital</i>

132
00:08:25.572 --> 00:08:27.856
<i>where he remains
in critical condition.</i>

133
00:08:27.924 --> 00:08:29.857
- I know this guy.
- You do?

134
00:08:29.926 --> 00:08:32.693
Yeah. when I used to take the
bus back when I lived with my dad.

135
00:08:32.762 --> 00:08:34.095
He was the driver.

136
00:08:35.331 --> 00:08:37.643
Can we talk about something
slightly more fun. please?

137
00:08:37.667 --> 00:08:40.907
Like. oh. where are we
going tomorrow night?

138
00:08:41.671 --> 00:08:45.151
You said you and Scott were
hanging out tomorrow night. right?

139
00:08:45.358 --> 00:08:48.660
Um. we were thinking of
what we were gonna do.

140
00:08:48.729 --> 00:08:51.891
Well. I am not sitting home
again watching lacrosse videos.

141
00:08:51.915 --> 00:08:55.183
so if the four of us are hanging
out. we are doing something fun.

142
00:08:55.852 --> 00:08:57.251
Hanging out?

143
00:08:58.121 --> 00:08:59.604
Like. the four of us?

144
00:08:59.673 --> 00:09:03.341
Do you wanna hang
out. like us and them?

145
00:09:03.410 --> 00:09:06.594
Yeah. I guess. Sounds fun.

146
00:09:06.663 --> 00:09:08.440
You know what else sounds fun?

147
00:09:08.464 --> 00:09:12.024
Stabbing myself in
the face with this fork.

148
00:09:12.786 --> 00:09:14.897
How about bowling?
You love to bowl.

149
00:09:14.921 --> 00:09:17.138
Yeah. with actual competition.

150
00:09:17.207 --> 00:09:20.942
How do you know we're
not actual competition?

151
00:09:21.011 --> 00:09:22.593
You can bowl. right?

152
00:09:23.763 --> 00:09:26.998
Sort of. Is it sort of. or yes?

153
00:09:27.550 --> 00:09:28.749
Yes.

154
00:09:30.620 --> 00:09:33.754
In fact. I'm a great bowler.

155
00:09:34.808 --> 00:09:36.274
You're a terrible bowler.

156
